# Zenr White Paper

## Abstract
Zenr is a meme coin designed to promote positivity and tranquility in the cryptocurrency space. With our beloved mascot, Zen Rabbit Usagiwa, we aim to create a community centered around relaxation, creativity, and enjoyment. 
By leveraging NFTs and hosting engaging events, Zenr seeks to cultivate an ecosystem that encourages chill vibes and fosters light-hearted interactions among participants.

